body:
Yoongi, Taehyung and Jungkook - Their friend makes a comment about your sex life

You groan in embarrassment as you tuck your face into your boyfriend’s neck. You’re spending times with his group today, since you’re all quite close, but the conversation has inevitably turned to sex. Namjoon is an incredibly dirty-minded man, and it seems that he just can’t stop himself from locking eyes with you and making a teasing comment about how sex must be with your boyfriend,

“I feel bad for you, seeing as he has a small dick and all. I’ve lived with him for years, I’ve seen it all,” He stage whispers, nodding in mock-sympathy.

Yoongi

Yoongi smirks, knowing that Namjoon’s only teasing. They’ve lived together for a long time, that much is true, but he has most definitely not seen it all, and so Namjoon couldn’t be more wrong. Yoongi knows this, you know this, all your neighbours probably know this, but the rest of the group seem to think it’s hilarious, and are all whooping and laughing to one another. Yoongi throws an arm around your shoulder lazily before looking at you innocently,

“I feel bad for you too, babe. I did have to help you walk here today,” Yoongi says softly, his natural pout becoming more pronounced through his teasing. You blush bright red at how true that is, and everyone in the group chokes on their own laughs, and then at how your facial expression confirms exactly what Yoongi was saying, “Eat your heart out, Namjoon,” He teases further, grinning over at his best friend.

Taehyung

For a few moments, Taehyung looks absolutely mortified. He thinks Namjoon is genuinely being serious, until the leader catches his eye and gives him a wink. Then the younger cops on, and feigns offence with a loud protest. Nobody hears it much over the laughs and teases being thrown around in the wake of Namjoon’s comment,

“Maybe we should let the lady speak for herself. You definitely didn’t think I was small last night did you? I’m surprised we didn’t get a noise complaint, you were screami-” Taehyung starts, until you slap a hand over his mouth so that he doesn’t finish that sentence. His eyes sparkle with mischief and love, and he licks the back of your hand childishly so you let go, “I’m not joking,” Taehyung whispers to only you, leaning down to kiss you gently, drowning out the childish uproar of his friends.

Jungkook

Everyone who knows Jungkook knows that his nickname is the Golden Maknae, and everyone who’s friends with him knows that such a nickname is well deserved. There’s really not much that your boyfriend can’t do, and sex is certainly no exception. He’s well aware of that, since you tell him so often (mainly in the moments afterwards and during). Namjoon’s teasing comment doesn’t offend him, and Jungkook doesn’t even break a sweat as he retorts,

“Whatever you want to think, hyung, go ahead. I think we might head out to a home store, though, and buy a new bed. Ours is broken,” Jungkook whines, almost innocent if it weren’t for the incredibly crude connotations of his words. Everyone splutters a little, before bursting out laughing so hard that they think they’ll never stop.

Masterlist

He’s never been a huge believer in fate, but the mention of Yoongi’s vision makes him consider the contrary, that he was meant to be with them, to take care of them.

Somehow, in only the short time he’s known them, they’ve made him feel unafraid of his magic for the first time.

In which Jung Hoseok is finally found.

blog.name: insidemyheadtoomanyquestionstm
blog.title: Green Tae and Honey
blog.description: I'm whipped for Kim Namjoon | GOT7, BTS, SKZ | Twice, Mamamoo, Red Velvet

body:
Kpop tag

FIRSTIES

First kpop group you listened to? 

SHINee

First group you actually knew the members’ names?

Also SHINee lmao

First bias ever? 

Onew (and guess what he is also from SHINee, I stanned only SHINee for like two years so the options for fristies are not that high)

First song to make you emotional?

Selene 6.23 (Do I even have to mention that its a SHINee song?

TOP 3

Top 3 favorite male groups

1. SHINee

2. Got7

3. Stray Kids

Top 3 favorite female groups

1. Mamamoo

(2. Twice

3. Red Velvet)

(I’m not really into girl groups but these two are the closest to ‘favorites’ if that makes sense lmao)

Top 3 favorite solo artists

1. Sunmi

2. Hyuna

3. Park Jimin

Top 3 songs of all time

1. SHINee – Tell me what to do

2. Got7 – You Are

3. BTS – Trivia: Love

Top 3 biases

1. RM/Kim Namjoon

2. Got7

3. Stray Kids

Top 3 fandoms you’re part of

1. Ahgase

2. Shawol

3. Stay

top 3 choreographies

1. Got7 – Just Right

2. BTS - Anpanman

3. Awkward Silence - Stray Kids

ULTIMATE

Ultimate bias group? 

SHINee or Got7 I can’t decide

Ultimate male bias? 

RM/Kim Namjoon (If the other members wouldn’t be a funny, i proably would be a solo stan for him)

Ultimate female bias? 

Solar

I got tagged by @minkey-jinki . I don’t really have anyone to tag so if you see it feel free to do it by yourself whatever
